    {
      "id": "sybil_18_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_18",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically sound E46 M3, powered by the iconic S54 3.2L inline-six featuring individual throttle bodies and a 7,900 RPM redline. This driver-spec example features the desirable 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox and a variable M differential lock. Critical preventative maintenance has been addressed, including a comprehensive VANOS overhaul and rear subframe reinforcement to ensure structural rigidity under lateral load. The suspension retains its factory-spec damping with refreshed bushings for precise turn-in. While the aesthetic reflects its 'good' status with minor road wear, the drivetrain remains robust and responsive. This is a high-performance chassis dialed for the purist who prioritizes mechanical excellence and linear power delivery.",
